title: Bug 121170: Inconsistent Column Labels Retrieval
description: The software should retrieve recognizable column labels from the metadata object both before and after extraction, but it's currently displaying different labels.
OB: When attempting to retrieve column labels from the metadata object before extraction, the system returns incorrect or unrecognizable strings. After extraction, the displayed labels differ from those retrieved before.
EB: The 'get column label' function should consistently retrieve user-recognizable strings from the metadata object before and after extraction. The labels displayed pre-extraction should match those displayed post-extraction.
SR:
1. Initialize meta data object with column labels.
2. Call getcolumnlabel before data extraction.
3. Verify that the returned labels are user recognizable and match the labels after data extraction.
